The paper discusses end-to-end learning of communication systems using deep neural network-based autoencoders, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT). The use of deep neural networks for optimization suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The mention of a feedback system and the use of reinforcement learning suggests a focus on control systems (cs.SY) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
